\id NAM
\h Naḥum
\toc1 Naḥum
\toc2 Naḥum
\toc3 Nḥm.
\mt1 Naḥum
\c 1
\s1 Awař n Naḥum x Ninwa
\m 
\v 1 Řḥukm issaggʷaden x Ninwa.
\m Adlis n řewḥiy n Naḥum, Alquci.\f ◼ \fr 1:1 \fk Naḥum\ft - isem wanita ixs ad yini ‘Afewwej’ niɣ ‘Amfewwej’.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 2 \bd Alif.\bd* - Arebbi ittasmen u SIDI intaqam,
\m SIDI d aneqqam u Netta d bab n wesɛar.
\m SIDI d aneqqam i řɛedyan nnes,
\m Netta igga řɛedyan jar tiṭṭawin nnes. \f ◼ \fr 1:2 \ft \bd afessar\bd* - adlis n Naḥum dayes ijj n uṣettef ‘AlifBat’. Man aya ixs ad yini aqa ɛřayen marra isekkilen (lḥuruf) n Tɛibranit ttwassxeddmen di tira-ya, ijj awarni i wenneɣni, kuř ijj di nnubet nnes. Ntaf ɣar umezwaru n kuř tasɣart ijj n usekkil (ijj n lḥarf) n lḥuruf n alifBat n Tmaziɣt ɣar uzeǧif n wawař amezwaru n ijj n wezyen n wawařen n wedlis. Ittwaf usettef-a waha deg Wedlis Iqeddsen n SIDI AREBBI, war iǧi deg uřa d ijj n wedlis nneɣni di Ccarq Amerwasu.\f*  \x ◘ \xo 1:2 \xt Uf. 20:5\x*
\m 
\v 3 SIDI ɣares ttasiɛ n řxaḍar
\m u jjehd nnes imɣar
\m u Netta war ittbarri ɛemmarṣ
\m \add wenni itteggen ddenb\add*.
\m \bd Bit.\bd* Abrid n SIDI di tḥaryaḍt
\m u deg usemmiḍ,
\m iseynuten aqa aten
\m d taɛejjajt n iḍaren nnes. \f ◼ \fr 1:3 \fk iseynuten ...\ft - am mammec iggur bnadem di tɛejjact, ammu iggur SIDI AREBBI x iseynuten n ijenwan.\f*
\b
\m 
\v 4 \bd Gimel.\bd* - Netta iwebbex řebḥar,
\m ittarra i-t yuẓeɣ,
\m marra iɣezran ittejja i-ten ttaẓɣen.
\m \bd Dalit.\bd* Bacan d Karmal sřawen,
\m uřa d nnuwar n Lubnan isřaw. \f ◼ \fr 1:4 \fk Bacan d Karmal ... Lubnan\ft - aqa-ten d jjwayeh s řɣiǧet aṭṭas deg wussan n zic.\f*
\m 
\v 5 \bd Hi.\bd* - Idurar ttarjijin zzayes,
\m u tiwririn fessyent,
\m \bd Waw.\bd* u tammurt tᵉttwassgeɛɛed-dd
\m zzat i wudem nnes,
\m uřa d marra wi xas izeddɣen! \x ◘ \xo 1:5 \xt Uf. 19:18; Izhd. 18:8; 29:5, 6; 97:4, 5; 114:4\x*
\m 
\v 6 \bd Zayin.\bd* - Wi izemmaren ad iqqim ibedd
\m zzat i wesxeḍ nnes,
\m u wi izemmaren ad ikkar
\m zzat i řḥaduq n weɣḍab nnes?
\m \bd Xit.\bd* Asɛar nnes ittwakebb-dd am tmessi
\m u tiṣuḍar ttwaqeǧɛent-i-dd zzayes.
\b
\m 
\v 7 \bd Tit.\bd* - Icna SIDI
\m i ddurri deg wass n řeḥṣaret.
\m \bd Yud.\bd* Netta issen marra
\m inni ɣares yarekkwařen. \x ◘ \xo 1:7 \xt Yuw. 4:16\x*
\b
\m 
\v 8 \bd Kaf.\bd* - \add S\add* yict n řḥemřet ifeyyḍen
\m ad yuqa amcan nnes
\m u řɛedyan nnes ad ten iḍfar,
\m \add ař ɣa yadfen ɣar\add* taǧest.
\b
\m 
\v 9 \bd Mim.\bd* - Min txarrṣem \add xenni\add* x SIDI?
\m Netta ad \add t\add* iqḍa qaɛ.
\m Aɣufi war dd-ittis martayen.
\m 
\v 10 Aqa nitni ttwamuden ɛad
\m am cbarq ak-d isennanen,
\m u ɣellan am yimescaren,
\m \add ammu\add* i ɣa ttwaccen nitni
\m qaɛ am uřum yuẓɣen.
\m 
\v 11 Zzayek i dd-iffeɣ
\m wenni ittxarrṣen
\m di min war iḥřin x SIDI,
\m amcawar i war isekkwin walu.
\b
\m 
\v 12 Ammu issawař SIDI:
\m Waxxa nitni ttfeřḥen
\m u \add ǧan\add* deg waṭṭas,
\m waxxa amenni nitni ad ttwaqessen
\m u netta ad iɛdu.
\m Waxxa necc ggiɣ xak aɣiř,
\m \add maca\add* necc war xak tteggeɣ aɣiř ɛad.
\m 
\v 13 Řexxu ad arẓeɣ azayřu nnes
\m \add i\add* xak \add immarsen\add*,
\m u Necc ad carrgeɣ tisɣunin nnec.
\b
\m 
\v 14 SIDI iweṣṣa xak,
\m aqa war zzayek
\m ittiři ɛad ḥed s yisem nnec.
\m Necc ad qeḍɛeɣ řexyařat ineqcen
\m d \add řexyařat\add* ifesyen zi taddart nnec.
\m Necc ad ggeɣ anḍeř nnec,
\m maɣar ufiɣ cek tefsused.
\b
\b
\c 2
\s1 Aweṭṭu n Ninwa
\m 
\v 1 Xzar, x idurar \add ttazzřen\add* iḍaren
\m n wenni dd-yiwyen řexbar aṣebḥan,
\m wenni ixebbaren s řehna.
\m Ɛeyyed řeɛyudat nnec, \add a\add* Yahuda,
\m seqfeř lwuɛud nnec,
\m maɣar wenni yareddǧen
\m war ittɣimi iẓekkwi xak ɛad,
\m netta inneqḍeɛ marra. \x ◘ \xo 2:1 \xt Ica. 52:7; Rum. 10:15\x*
\m 
\v 2 Ijjen wenni yuẓẓřen \add x iwdan\add* s lɛunf
\m i dd-igeɛɛed xak!
\m Ɛess x lburj, ḥḍa abrid,
\m semḥeḍ tijɛinna nnec,
\m arni di jjhed nnec!
\b
\m 
\v 3 S minzi SIDI ad dd-yarr
\m řɛezz n Yaɛqub,
\m \add aqa-t d\add* řɛezz n Israil.
\m Maɣar ikeccaḍen keccḍen ten,
\m u nitni ɣeḍřen tizermin nsen. \x ◘ \xo 2:3 \xt Izhd. 80:13; Ica. 10:12\x*
\m 
\v 4 Tcappat \add n useřqi\add*
\m n ayt n bu-teɣruḍt zewɣent,
\m iryazen imeḥḍen \add bedden\add*
\m sswejden i umenɣi
\m \add s warruḍ\add* azeggʷaɣ iḥedqen,
\m ɣar \add tessiqt n\add* tmessi n wuzzař
\m n ikarruten \add n umenɣi\add*,
\m deg wass i di i ɣa issewjed ixef nnes
\m u \add ticejjura n\add* umerzi ad nnhezzen. \f ◼ \fr 2:4 \fk amerzi\ft - niɣ ‘ameḍzi’.\f*
\m 
\v 5 Ikarruten n umenɣi hajen deg ibriden,
\m aqa ẓẓeɛwaḍen zi ssa ɣar da
\m deg wazzayen,
\m ttwaḍharen am yiṣefḍawen,
\m nitni gemmaren da d diha am wassamen.
\m 
\v 6 Netta ittxarreṣ deg ayt n jjehd,
\m nitni \add maca\add* ttneqraḍen am gguren
\m nitni ttazzřen ɣar řḥiḍ nsen,
\m \add mani\add* ibedd ssqef \add n uhjam\add* iwjed.
\b
\m 
\v 7 Tiwwura n iɣezran nnurezment,
\m u řeqṣar ad ifsi.
\m 
\v 8 Aqa tamesřact tbedd nican!
\m Nettat ad tᵉttwaɛarra,
\m ad tᵉttwassgeɛɛed,
\m u tiyya nnes sɣuyyunt
\m amecnaw abarri n tedbirin,
\m \add am\add* ccatent deg idmaren nsent. \f ◼ \fr 2:8 \fk deg idmaren nsent\ft - s Tɛibranit ‘deg wuřawen nsent’.\f*
\m 
\v 9 Ninwa am yijj n uyeřmam n waman
\m zeg wass i di iǧa.
\m \add Řexxu maca\add* arekkweřen nitni.
\m Beddem! Beddem!, \add ttřaɣan nitni\add*,
\m \add maca\add* uřa d ijj war dd-ittneqřib.
\m 
\v 10 Keccḍem nnuqart, keccḍem ureɣ!
\m War din qeṭṭu i řeknuz,
\m ɣar ucewwar n ɛřam kuř řeqcuɛ.
\m 
\v 11 Texwa, tᵉttwakecceḍ
\m u tᵉttwareddeǧ nettat,
\m uř ifsi uca ifadden fecřen,
\m ttekksent as tijɛinna marra
\m u iɣembab nsen warɣen marra. \x ◘ \xo 2:11 \xt Aɛwd. 1:28; 20:8; Yac. 2:11; 5:1; 7:5; Ica. 13:8, 7; 21:3; Ḥiz. 21:12\x*
\m 
\v 12 Mani iǧa řexxu řmargeḥ n wayraden,
\m d řmedweř n wayraden imeẓyanen,
\m mani yuyur weyrad,
\m aqa-tt d tayradt ak-d weyrad ameẓyan
\m \add am\add* uřa d ijj issnexřeɛ i-ten?
\m 
\v 13 \add Mani iǧa řexxu\add* wayrad nni imezzqen
\m min ḥdajen tarwa nnes
\m u ijeyyef i tayradin nnes,
\m d wenni iccuren ifran nnes s ukecceḍ,
\m d imucan nnes n udurri
\m zi min ittwacarrgen?
\b
\m 
\v 14 Xzar, \add Necc ad iřiɣ\add* xak,
\m \add ammu i\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat,
\m Necc ad arreɣ ikarruten nnec d ddexxan.
\m Ad cceɣ ssif iyraden nnec imeẓyanen,
\m u Necc ad qeḍɛeɣ takeccaḍt nnec
\m zi temmurt
\m u ɛemmarṣ ɛad ad tᵉttwaseř
\m tmijja n ireqqasen nnec. \f ◼ \fr 2:14 \fk tmijja n ireqqasen nnec\ft - xzar Ica. 36:13, 37:9.\f*
\b
\b
\c 3
\m 
\v 1 \bd Uct x tendint n idammen!\bd*
\m Aqa-tt d axarriq d lɛunf marra,
\m tukkarḍa war tᵉttbeddi ca. \f ◼ \fr 3:1 \fk tandint n idammen\ft - ixs ad yini aqa tandint-a teccur s usizzeř n idammen.\f*
\m 
\v 2 Řḥess n urekkuḍ,
\m řḥess n uqarqeb n tjarrarin,
\m iysan ittazzřen deg wenneḍ
\m d ikarruten ineṭṭwen.
\m 
\v 3 Amennay inya,
\m ssif ittwesseg,
\m fřitca \add aqa-tt\add* am wassam.
\m Aṭṭas d inni ittwanɣen
\m u \add aqa din\add* aɛurric n imettan,
\m řxecbat war ɣarsent řḥed,
\m \add wah\add*, ttenqraḍen di řxecbat nsen.
\m 
\v 4 Zi ssibbet n waṭṭas n farq-ccɣeř
\m n temɣart řmuḥesna,
\m n lalla n tseḥḥart,
\m tenni izznuzan řegnus s farq-ccɣeř nnes
\m uřa d \add marra\add* řaǧat s useḥḥar nnes,
\m 
\v 5 xzar, \add s uya ad xam iřiɣ\add*,
\m \add ammu\add* iqqar SIDI n řɛeskarat,
\m u Necc ad ssgeɛɛdeɣ
\m timuwwa \add n warruḍ nnem\add*
\m tiwwa i uɣembub nnem,
\m u Necc ad ssecneɣ i řegnus tuɛɛaryent nnem,
\m u řefḍiḥet nnem i tgeldiwin.
\m 
\v 6 Necc ad cem řeqfeɣ s nnɛawat,
\m u ad cem ssfeḍḥeɣ
\m u ad cem arreɣ i usfurrej.
\m 
\v 7 Xenni ad imsar
\m aqa man wen cem i ɣa iẓaren,
\m ad zzayem yarweř, ad yini
\m “\add Tandint n\add* Ninwa txarreb!
\m Wi zzayes i ɣa iceḍnen?”
\m Mani d am i ɣa yarzuɣ
\m inni cem i ɣa issfewwjen?
\b
\m 
\v 8 Ma cem ḥsen zi Nu-Amun
\m nni ittɣiman ɣar iɣezran,
\m am d as qewwaren waman,
\m \add ařami\add* řebḥar d acbar nnes n zzat,
\m \add aqa\add* řḥiḍ nnes igeɛɛed zi řebḥar.
\m 
\v 9 Kuc tuɣa d ṣṣulṭa nnes, uřa d Misřa,
\m war tuɣi ɣares aneggar.
\m Fuṭ d ayt n Libiya
\m tuɣa aten zeg imɛawnen nnec.
\m 
\v 10 Uřa d nettat tuyur di lmenfa,
\m di tmeḥbast.
\m Uřa d iḥenjiren nnes ttwařebzen
\m di tɣemmura n marra n tebridin,
\m u x imcennɛen nnes
\m nḍaren xasen taqedduḥt
\m u marra imɣaren nnes
\m ttwacarfen s ssnaseř.
\b
\m 
\v 11 Uřa d cem ad tescared
\m ad tessnuffared ixef nnem.
\m Ɛawed cem ad tarzud ijj n lburj
\m \add i udurri\add* zi řeɛdu nnem.
\m 
\v 12 Marra lqelɛat nnem am wurtan
\m ak-d řbacur.
\m Mařa ttwanhezzen,
\m ad wḍan deg uqemmum
\m n wenni ixsen ad ten yecc.
\m 
\v 13 Xzar, aqa d wa d řgens nnem,
\m \add aqa-t d\add* timɣarin.
\m Ttnurzment tewwura n temmurt nnem
\m qaɛ i řeɛdu,
\m timessi ad tecc iɛumad nnem i ubelleɛ.
\b
\m 
\v 14 Ayem aman i yixef nnem i řeḥṣaret,
\m semten lqelɛat nnem,
\m bedd di třaxt,
\m ɛefs di tarrist,
\m seqseḥ iẓra ittwassuydan!
\m 
\v 15 Timessi ad cem tecc din,
\m ssif ad cem ineɣ,
\m ad cem tecc am bu-weřsaḥ!
\m Arni deg ixef nnem am bu-weřsaḥ,
\m arni deg yixef nnem am tmurɣi.
\m 
\v 16 Cek tessmarnid deg isebbaben nnem
\m ktar zeg itran n ujenna.
\m Bu-weřsaḥ ad issars tiřmect nnes
\m uca ad iḍwa.
\m 
\v 17 Tarwa n taṣiřet nnem
\m am yijj n weyřaf n tmurɣi
\m u řɛeskarat nnem
\m am yixenfusen imeqqranen,
\m inni yarsan di řeḥyuḍ
\m deg yijj n wass d aṣemmaḍ.
\m Řami dd-tenqar tfuct,
\m ṭṭawen ssenni deɣya.
\m War issin ḥed amcan nsen.
\m Mani ruḥen nitni?
\m 
\v 18 Imeksawen nnec ttnudumen,
\m \add aya,\add* ajeǧid n Accur,
\m ayt n jjehd nnec ttᵉṭṭṣen,
\m řgens nnec ad t zeǧɛen x idurar,
\m uca uřa d ijjen war \add ten\add* issmun ca.
\m 
\v 19 War din asgenfi i tareẓẓit nnec,
\m ittekkes ac uyezzim!
\m Marra inni i xak isřin řexbar,
\m ad ccaten deg ifassen zi ssibbet nnec,
\m maɣar x man wen
\m war iɛeddu ca řebda řɣar nnec? 
